2026-02-28T12:13:23.226790Z  INFO session_loop{thread_id=019ca410-fbfa-7f13-be33-f83185c604c5}: codex_core::stream_events_utils: ToolCall: exec_command {"cmd":"cat > /Users/valeriy/Projects/speckit-test/specs/001-todo-daily-focus/tasks.md <<'EOF'\n# Tasks: Daily Focus Todo Manager\n\n**Input**: Design documents from `/specs/001-todo-daily-focus/`\n**Prerequisites**: plan.md (required), spec.md (required for user stories), research.md, data-model.md, contracts/\n\n**Tests**: Tests are REQUIRED for every user story and behavior change.\n\n**Organization**: Tasks are grouped by user story to enable independent implementation and testing of each story.\n\n## Format: `[ID] [P?] [Story] Description`\n\n- **[P]**: Can run in parallel (different files, no dependencies)\n- **[Story]**: Which user story this task belongs to (e.g., US1, US2, US3)\n- Include exact file paths in descriptions\n\n## Path Conventions\n\n- **Web app**: `backend/src/`, `frontend/src/`\n- Tests: `backend/tests/`, `frontend/tests/`\n\n## Phase 1: Setup (Shared Infrastructure)\n\n**Purpose**: Project initialization and basic structure\n\n- [ ] T001 Create project directory skeleton in `backend/src/api/`, `backend/src/db/`, `backend/src/services/`, `backend/src/models/`, `backend/tests/contract/`, `backend/tests/integration/`, `backend/tests/unit/`, `frontend/src/components/`, `frontend/src/pages/`, `frontend/src/services/`, `frontend/src/styles/`, `frontend/tests/e2e/`, `frontend/tests/unit/`, and `data/.gitkeep`\n- [ ] T002 Initialize root workspace scripts and shared tooling config in `package.json`\n- [ ] T003 [P] Initialize backend package and TypeScript config in `backend/package.json` and `backend/tsconfig.json`\n- [ ] T004 [P] Initialize Vite vanilla TypeScript frontend and Bootstrap dependency in `frontend/package.json`, `frontend/tsconfig.json`, and `frontend/vite.config.ts`\n- [ ] T005 [P] Configure linting and formatting in `.eslintrc.cjs`, `.prettierrc`, and `.eslintignore`\n- [ ] T006 [P] Configure environment templates and SQLite path defaults in `.env.example` and `backend/src/config.ts`\n\n---\n\n## Phase 2: Foundational (Blocking Prerequisites)\n\n**Purpose**: Core infrastructure that MUST be complete before ANY user story can be implemented\n\n**⚠️ CRITICAL**: No user story work can begin until this phase is complete\n\n- [ ] T007 Create SQLite schema and initialization SQL in `backend/src/db/schema.sql` and `backend/src/db/initDb.ts`\n- [ ] T008 [P] Implement SQLite client and repository utilities in `backend/src/db/client.ts` and `backend/src/db/repository.ts`\n- [ ] T009 [P] Define shared domain models and DTOs in `backend/src/models/inboxPoint.ts`, `backend/src/models/todoItem.ts`, `backend/src/models/dailySession.ts`, and `frontend/src/services/types.ts`\n- [ ] T010 Implement lifecycle rule helpers (stale thresholds and transition guards) in `backend/src/services/lifecycleRules.ts`\n- [ ] T011 [P] Setup Express app, routing registration, and global error handling in `backend/src/app.ts`, `backend/src/server.ts`, and `backend/src/middleware/errorHandler.ts`\n- [ ] T012 [P] Implement app state bootstrap endpoint in `backend/src/api/appState.ts` and register it in `backend/src/api/index.ts`\n- [ ] T013 Configure testing infrastructure in `backend/vitest.config.ts`, `frontend/vitest.config.ts`, `frontend/playwright.config.ts`, and `backend/tests/helpers/testDb.ts`\n- [ ] T014 Create base SPA shell and mode-aware layout in `frontend/src/main.ts`, `frontend/src/components/AppLayout.ts`, and `frontend/src/styles/app.css`\n\n**Checkpoint**: Foundation ready - user story implementation can now begin in parallel\n\n---\n\n## Phase 3: User Story 1 - Daily Review and Planning (Priority: P1) 🎯 MVP\n\n**Goal**: Let users start in Daily Review mode, create todos from inbox points, and build today’s daily list.\n\n**Independent Test**: Open app, add inbox points, create todos from points, assign selected todos to today’s list, and verify the daily list contents are correct.\n\n### Tests for User Story 1 (REQUIRED) ✅\n\n- [ ] T015 [P] [US1] Add contract tests for inbox point and todo creation/list endpoints in `backend/tests/contract/us1-planning.contract.test.ts`\n- [ ] T016 [P] [US1] Add integration test for creating todos from points and assigning daily items in `backend/tests/integration/us1-planning-flow.test.ts`\n- [ ] T017 [P] [US1] Add end-to-end Daily Review flow test in `frontend/tests/e2e/us1-daily-review.spec.ts`\n\n### Implementation for User Story 1\n\n- [ ] T018 [US1] Implement inbox point create/list API in `backend/src/api/inboxPoints.ts`\n- [ ] T019 [US1] Implement todo create/list API with inbox linkage in `backend/src/api/todos.ts`\n- [ ] T020 [US1] Implement daily-list assignment API in `backend/src/api/dailyList.ts`\n- [ ] T021 [P] [US1] Build Daily Review page and inbox point entry form in `frontend/src/pages/DailyReviewPage.ts`\n- [ ] T022 [P] [US1] Build inbox point card and daily list selection components in `frontend/src/components/InboxPointCard.ts` and `frontend/src/components/DailyListPanel.ts`\n- [ ] T023 [US1] Implement review-mode API client/store wiring in `frontend/src/services/apiClient.ts` and `frontend/src/services/reviewStore.ts`\n- [ ] T024 [US1] Add Daily Review validation and error-state UI in `frontend/src/components/InlineError.ts` and `frontend/src/pages/DailyReviewPage.ts`\n\n**Checkpoint**: User Story 1 is fully functional and testable independently\n\n---\n\n## Phase 4: User Story 2 - Focus Mode Execution (Priority: P2)\n\n**Goal**: Let users switch into Focus mode, see only today’s todos, and keep completed items visible with strikethrough.\n\n**Independent Test**: After selecting daily items, switch to Focus mode, complete an item, and confirm it remains visible with completed styling.\n\n### Tests for User Story 2 (REQUIRED) ✅\n\n- [ ] T025 [P] [US2] Add contract tests for mode update and todo status update APIs in `backend/tests/contract/us2-focus-mode.contract.test.ts`\n- [ ] T026 [P] [US2] Add integration test for focus-mode completion visibility behavior in `backend/tests/integration/us2-focus-flow.test.ts`\n- [ ] T027 [P] [US2] Add end-to-end Focus mode workflow test in `frontend/tests/e2e/us2-focus-mode.spec.ts`\n\n### Implementation for User Story 2\n\n- [ ] T028 [US2] Implement mode persistence/update API in `backend/src/api/mode.ts` and `backend/src/services/sessionService.ts`\n- [ ] T029 [US2] Implement todo completion/reopen status transitions in `backend/src/services/todoService.ts` and `backend/src/api/todos.ts`\n- [ ] T030 [P] [US2] Build Focus mode page for daily-list-only display in `frontend/src/pages/FocusPage.ts`\n- [ ] T031 [P] [US2] Implement completed-item strikethrough rendering in `frontend/src/components/TodoListItem.ts` and `frontend/src/styles/status.css`\n- [ ] T032 [US2] Wire mode switching and focus data loading in `frontend/src/components/ModeToggle.ts` and `frontend/src/services/focusStore.ts`\n\n**Checkpoint**: User Stories 1 and 2 both work independently\n\n---\n\n## Phase 5: User Story 3 - Aging, Requeue, and Trash Lifecycle (Priority: P3)\n\n**Goal**: Enforce end-of-day rollover, stale highlighting, automatic trash movement after unchanged stale period, and persistent trash access.\n\n**Independent Test**: Simulate age thresholds and rollover; verify inbox requeue, red stale marking, auto-trash behavior, and trash accessibility.\n\n### Tests for User Story 3 (REQUIRED) ✅\n\n- [ ] T033 [P] [US3] Add contract tests for rollover and trash endpoints in `backend/tests/contract/us3-lifecycle.contract.test.ts`\n- [ ] T034 [P] [US3] Add integration tests for stale-marking and auto-trash rules in `backend/tests/integration/us3-lifecycle-rules.test.ts`\n- [ ] T035 [P] [US3] Add end-to-end lifecycle and trash flow test in `frontend/tests/e2e/us3-lifecycle-trash.spec.ts`\n\n### Implementation for User Story 3\n\n- [ ] T036 [US3] Implement end-of-day rollover endpoint and requeue logic in `backend/src/api/rollover.ts` and `backend/src/services/lifecycleService.ts`\n- [ ] T037 [US3] Implement stale-marking and auto-trash eligibility processing in `backend/src/services/lifecycleService.ts`\n- [ ] T038 [US3] Implement trash list API in `backend/src/api/trash.ts`\n- [ ] T039 [P] [US3] Add stale red-state rendering in `frontend/src/components/TodoListItem.ts` and `frontend/src/styles/status.css`\n- [ ] T040 [P] [US3] Build trash page and navigation entry in `frontend/src/pages/TrashPage.ts` and `frontend/src/components/AppNav.ts`\n- [ ] T041 [US3] Trigger lifecycle recalculation on startup/state refresh in `backend/src/server.ts` and `frontend/src/services/appState.ts`\n\n**Checkpoint**: All user stories are independently functional\n\n---\n\n## Phase 6: Polish & Cross-Cutting Concerns\n\n**Purpose**: Improvements that affect multiple user stories\n\n- [ ] T042 [P] Document concrete run/test steps in `specs/001-todo-daily-focus/quickstart.md`\n- [ ] T043 Refine naming, error messages, and type strictness in `backend/src/services/todoService.ts`, `backend/src/services/lifecycleService.ts`, `frontend/src/pages/DailyReviewPage.ts`, and `frontend/src/pages/FocusPage.ts`\n- [ ] T044 Validate performance budget with benchmark test in `backend/tests/integration/performance-view-load.test.ts` and record results in `specs/001-todo-daily-focus/quickstart.md`\n- [ ] T045 [P] Add boundary-focused unit tests in `backend/tests/unit/dateBoundaries.test.ts` and `frontend/tests/unit/modeState.test.ts`\n- [ ] T046 [P] Add UX consistency checklist for implemented states in `specs/001-todo-daily-focus/checklists/ux-consistency.md`\n- [ ] T047 Harden input validation and request-size protections in `backend/src/middleware/security.ts` and `backend/src/app.ts`\n- [ ] T048 Run end-to-end quickstart validation and capture evidence in `specs/001-todo-daily-focus/quickstart-validation.md`\n\n---\n\n## Dependencies & Execution Order\n\n### Phase Dependencies\n\n- **Setup (Phase 1)**: No dependencies - can start immediately\n- **Foundational (Phase 2)**: Depends on Setup completion - BLOCKS all user stories\n- **User Stories (Phase 3+)**: Depend on Foundational completion\n- **Polish (Phase 6)**: Depends on all desired user stories being complete\n\n### User Story Dependencies\n\n- **User Story 1 (P1)**: Starts immediately after Foundational and defines MVP behavior\n- **User Story 2 (P2)**: Depends on US1 daily-list data flow and API contracts\n- **User Story 3 (P3)**: Depends on US1/US2 state model and status transitions\n\n### Within Each User Story\n\n- Tests MUST be written and FAIL before implementation\n- API/domain logic before UI wiring\n- Status/lifecycle validation before final integration\n- Story must pass its independent test before moving to next priority\n\n### Parallel Opportunities\n\n- T003-T006 can run in parallel during setup\n- T008, T009, T011, T012 can run in parallel in Foundational phase after T007 where needed\n- Per story, contract/integration/e2e tests can run in parallel\n- Per story, UI component tasks marked [P] can run in parallel with non-overlapping files\n\n---\n\n## Parallel Example: User Story 1\n\n```bash\nTask: \"T015 [US1] Contract tests in backend/tests/contract/us1-planning.contract.test.ts\"\nTask: \"T016 [US1] Integration tests in backend/tests/integration/us1-planning-flow.test.ts\"\nTask: \"T017 [US1] E2E tests in frontend/tests/e2e/us1-daily-review.spec.ts\"\n```\n\n## Parallel Example: User Story 2\n\n```bash\nTask: \"T030 [US2] Build Focus page in frontend/src/pages/FocusPage.ts\"\nTask: \"T031 [US2] Add strikethrough UI state in frontend/src/components/TodoListItem.ts and frontend/src/styles/status.css\"\n```\n\n## Parallel Example: User Story 3\n\n```bash\nTask: \"T039 [US3] Add stale red-state rendering in frontend/src/components/TodoListItem.ts\"\nTask: \"T040 [US3] Build trash page in frontend/src/pages/TrashPage.ts and frontend/src/components/AppNav.ts\"\n```\n\n---\n\n## Implementation Strategy\n\n### MVP First (User Story 1 Only)\n\n1. Complete Phase 1 and Phase 2\n2. Complete Phase 3 (US1)\n3. Validate independent test for US1\n4. Demo daily review planning workflow\n\n### Incremental Delivery\n\n1. Deliver US1 (daily planning)\n2. Deliver US2 (focus execution)\n3. Deliver US3 (lifecycle automation and trash)\n4. Run polish tasks and finalize quickstart validation\n\n### Parallel Team Strategy\n\n1. One developer focuses backend lifecycle/services\n2. One developer focuses frontend pages/components\n3. One developer focuses automated tests/contracts\n4. Integrate at phase checkpoints only after required tests pass\n\n---\n\n## Notes\n\n- [P] tasks = different files, no dependencies\n- [Story] labels map tasks to user stories for traceability\n- Each story is independently completable and testable\n- Keep SQLite file path fixed at `data/todo.db`\n- Avoid adding frameworks beyond planned minimal dependencies\nEOF","workdir":"/Users/valeriy/Projects/speckit-test"} thread_id=019ca410-fbfa-7f13-be33-f83185c604c5
