2026-02-28T12:19:35.696794Z  INFO session_loop{thread_id=019ca410-fbfa-7f13-be33-f83185c604c5}: codex_core::stream_events_utils: ToolCall: exec_command {"cmd":"sed -n '1,260p' /Users/valeriy/Projects/speckit-test/specs/001-todo-daily-focus/plan.md","workdir":"/Users/valeriy/Projects/speckit-test","max_output_tokens":12000} thread_id=019ca410-fbfa-7f13-be33-f83185c604c5
